1325:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @brief  Initializes the TIM PWM Time Base according to the specified
1326:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         parameters in the TIM_HandleTypeDef and initializes the associated handle.
1327:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @note   Switching from Center Aligned counter mode to Edge counter mode (or reverse)
